<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2313] Add VERBOSE to LuceneTestCase and LuceneTestCaseJ4</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2313</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;component-build.xml allows to define tests.verbose as a system property when running tests. Both LuceneTestCase and LuceneTestCaseJ4 don&apos;t read that property. It will be useful for overriding tests to access one place for this setting (I believe currently some tests do it on their own). Then (as a separate issue) we can move all tests that don&apos;t check the parameter to only print if VERBOSE is true.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will post a patch soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
